{"TopicId":164405,"ForumId":15,"TopicTitle":"Specular map","CreatedByName":"Da_Pedro","CreatedById":158860,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-14T09:22:51Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Da_Pedro","CreatedById":158860,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-14T09:22:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello guys !\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nI\u0027m currently working with \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/178977-huxtus/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022178977\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/178977-huxtus/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@HuXTUS\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0on a part.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nAdding a diffuse and a bump/normal map is very easy but what\u0027s up about specular ?\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nShaders have no slot for that. I just found an 1 year old discussion about that :\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/143781-specular-maps/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it still the way to add specular ? And moreover, does someone has a great tutorial on how to add this alpha channel to the diffuse (not sure it works with JPG\u00A0and PNG should be a mess for the game, no ?)\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHope to see some help quickly \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/uploads/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nThanks \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/uploads/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kurld","CreatedById":79950,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-14T18:59:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s still the way, as far as I know.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you use Gimp, I was actually looking at this earlier and there\u0027s a pretty good explanation of how to modify a stock part\u0027s dds part\u00A0way down the first page.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/143324-need-a-tiny-bit-of-help-getting-started/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ger_space","CreatedById":167349,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-18T20:44:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223147947\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022164405\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221502702571\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158860\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Da_Pedro\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn \u200E14\u200E.\u200E08\u200E.\u200E2017 at 11:22 AM, Da_Pedro said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello guys !\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nI\u0027m currently working with \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/178977-huxtus/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022178977\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/178977-huxtus/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@HuXTUS\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0on a part.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nAdding a diffuse and a bump/normal map is very easy but what\u0027s up about specular ?\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nShaders have no slot for that. I just found an 1 year old discussion about that :\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/143781-specular-maps/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it still the way to add specular ? And moreover, does someone has a great tutorial on how to add this alpha channel to the diffuse (not sure it works with JPG\u00A0and PNG should be a mess for the game, no ?)\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHope to see some help quickly \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nThanks \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor a specular map you need a custom shader which supports them and make \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/161898-13texturereplacerreplaced-v04/\u0026amp;\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003ETRR\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E support this.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCurrently the shader of TRR has reflectivity on its diffuse (Color) map Alpha channel and transparancy on the emissive map Alpha channel. so the two Basic maps are used up. (normal map Alpha cannot be used, because of unity packing format)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou could request the Addition of a third map to TRR or a different shader, which uses the Alpha channel of the emissive map for the specular Information (but will be never transparent)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Da_Pedro","CreatedById":158860,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-18T22:18:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a reallygood idea, I\u0027ll dig in, thank you man ! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think we\u0027ll just realease a basic part with a general glossy, and update it later \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-08-18T22:19:07Z\u0022 title=\u002208/18/2017 10:19  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 18, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Da_Pedro\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}